Comment: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:31.05,op jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.97,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.52,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.19,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Tell me what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:54.57,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.45,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Looking for the escape from pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:01.83,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:05.29,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:09.04,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:12.59,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:15.93,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:19.51,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}May be it's already too late to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.89,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.19,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:29.69,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:31.44,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}It's not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:39.16,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:44.20,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.54,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}we'll make it in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:52.84,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.21,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I know who I am
Comment: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:42.98,op ch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.97,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}命運將我們引領至此 並看着我跳戰不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.52,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}感覺我墮入了謊言的火焰中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.19,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}說出你對我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:54.57,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}盡力不去走回頭路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.45,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}探求走出痛苦的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:01.83,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我合十雙手去祈求不必犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:05.29,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}這是我和你的希望所訂下的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:09.04,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在時機成熟前做好出擊的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:12.59,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}去追趕那個浮現出來的黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:15.93,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}放棄那個讓我單獨一人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:19.51,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}或許這已經太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.89,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要捨去作為命運的那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.19,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沒有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:29.69,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}若我能修補錯誤並將你救出苦海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:31.44,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}這並不足以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:39.16,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}並不足以讓我打破這世界的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:44.20,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我絕不離開你 絕不想失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.54,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們來結束這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:52.84,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}別再退縮 這輩子我不會跟隨別人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.21,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我知道自己是誰
Comment: 0,0:28:02.44,0:28:02.48,ed jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.26,0:28:19.03,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}壊れないように優しく抱いて　溶けて涙流す
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.60,0:28:30.23,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}そんな氷の人形みたいに なれないから
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.66,0:28:44.46,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}もう逃げない　知りたいの　強く
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.46,0:28:46.16,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}―I believe…believe in you―
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.16,0:28:50.26,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}きっと一番の約束の言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.26,0:28:54.66,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}痛いくらい握って離さない
